SHE NEVER HAS.

168
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,800
YOU NEED TO STOP THIS.

169
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:54,800
YOU'RE IN EARLY,
WHAT'S UP?

170
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:56,900
