AFTER THE DANCE?

171
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:58,200
NOPE. NOTHING.

172
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:00,400
OH, BUMMER.
WHY NOT?

173
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:02,000
