OF HIM AND THINKS HE'S BAD NEWS.

183
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:24,300
SO ANY IDEA
WHO THESPEOPLE ARE?

184
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:26,600
NED KNEW THE GIRL.
KRISTY FROM ORCHESTRA.

185
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,700
BUT THAT'S ALL I KNOW.

186
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,200
THERE WE GO.

187
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:32,100
IT'S DEFINITELY MY GHOST.

188
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:35,900
DEBORAH MARKS.
SHE DIED A MONTH AGO,

189
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:37,500
AN ACCIDENT AT THE HOME.

190
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:40,100
WOW. THAT IS SOME
POWER COUPLE.

191
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,900
